            <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #4caf50;">-25%</div>
            <div style="color: #ccc; font-size: 0.95rem;">Km percorsi al giorno<br>con percorsi ottimizzati</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
          <div style="background: #1a1a1a; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; border-top: 3px solid #ffd600;">
            <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #ffd600;">-95%</div>
            <div style="color: #ccc; font-size: 0.95rem;">Contestazioni clienti<br>grazie a foto e firma</div>
          </div>
        </div>
